  "description": "Instance inventory and state breakdown for OpenStack Nova from openstack-exporter: how many servers are ACTIVE, SHUTOFF, ERROR or stuck in a transitional state, and how they split across projects. Answers \"what is the fleet of instances actually doing, and which ones need attention?\".",
